  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "The KL CYC S is the perfect fixture for smooth and even cyclorama, set and wall washing applications. It utilizes a carefully crafted asymmetrical reflector design to achieve perfect blends while covering significant heights with ease. \nDesigned with an incredibly low profile housing the KL CYC is also the ideal choice for footlight positions, providing excellent versatility for stage, film, television and event lighting use.\nSeamless magnetic alignment, simple mounting bracket attachment and elegant power and data wire management make the KL CYC a breeze to integrate into new designs or upgrade traditional CYC fixtures or foot ramps to a modern LED fixture without compromises.",
